protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Demolition of existing buildings at Nos.171 and 175 Seymour Place and erection of a part six, part seven storey building comprising 66 self-contained affordable housing units with associated basement floor providing 32 parking spaces and 64 cycle parking spaces. Associated new landscaping, erection of parking canopy, installation of car lift to basement car park and provision of children's play area to rear. ('Classical' Scheme).
